    <item>
      <title>美国债务达到令人担忧的里程碑，专家表示特朗普的政策可能会使情况变得更糟</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/07/business/us-debt-trump-policies-budget.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[债务增长超过了美国经济规模。专家表示，除非政策制定者进行干预，否则总统的政策可能会加剧该国的财政难题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/07/business/us-debt-trump-policies-budget.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 May 2026 17:31:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>为什么股票和债券对伊朗战争的反应不同</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/07/business/stocks-bonds-markets-iran-war.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[股票投资者押注，尽管有战争，公司仍将获得巨额利润。但包括美国国债在内的债券投资者还有其他担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/07/business/stocks-bonds-markets-iran-war.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 May 2026 16:37:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>汉坦病毒反应表明特朗普的削减措施如何损害了美国的准备工作</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/07/health/hantavirus-americans-cdc.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特朗普政府削减了传染病研究的资金，并且用于应对疫情的员工（包括疾病侦探）大幅减少。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/07/health/hantavirus-americans-cdc.html</guid>
